{"tid":2160917,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會議員是「筍工」 月薪津貼有幾多？","createTime":"2020-08-17T09:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T05:16:51.000Z","uid":118346,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ed9f82792b02451f347f4d80a07f949ff72419c0","tid":2160917,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1475000/1476889/concil_thumb_201608081_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1475000%2F1476889%2Fconcil_thumb_201608081_1024.jpg&h=1982da22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f85bad2123301e0dbb2b407c823679700af0c9dd","tid":2160917,"uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:17:41.000Z","msg":"議員助理人工有幾多？<br />\n<br />\n經濟日報曾報道部分政黨的議員助理平均薪酬，當中建制派政黨議員「出手」較高，以劉皇發一位議員助理為例，月薪達7萬多元。<br />\n<br />\n若以平均月薪計算，經民聯議員出手較濶綽，議員助理平均薪酬有2.7萬元。其次是自由黨，助理月薪平均有2.4萬元；第三是民建聯，平均1.9萬元；至於工聯會的助理薪酬則較低，平均月薪有1.5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">其他泛民政黨，如民主黨、公民黨、人民力量等，其議員助理平均薪酬約1.3萬至1.4萬元。</span><br />\n<br />\n按新一屆立法會議員薪津安排調整，每名立法會議員每年可獲發約255萬元作為辦事處營運開支，比上屆增加7%。開支包括職員薪酬、辦事處租金等，議員申報開支需有單據證明，實報實銷。<br />\n<br />\n雖然各議員可申報的津貼上限都一樣，但指引並沒有規定議員助理的薪酬標準，因此議員助理的薪酬懸殊。"},{"pid":"0197e5d1ec83469977acb8efb5a3e92131dd2208","tid":2160917,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3deab6edb047c0ce86fdab20b739224a3361f391","tid":2160917,"uid":118346,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n四年過千萬，唔怪得咁多人做政工作者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac